project: Quick! Help me get all the mice! I am really hungry.

You are a hungry potato cat. You need to eat all the mice and avoid falling to move to the next level. 
Use the arrow keys to move. If you are using a phone, tilt it to move, and tap to jump. 
Have fun!
The red blocks will kill you. Make sure you don't touch them!
Be careful! There are hungry dogs running around who want to eat you! Avoid them by jumping over them.
You won! Great Job! Thank you for helping me get food!
